column5: This custom built villa with over-sized balcony located in Oak Shores on Lake Austin community and is 30 mins away from downtown Austin. This unique home on 1.07 wooded acres offers privacy, has a gated driveway, and is located close to Ski Shores Marina. With a fairy-tale ambience, you'll find dark wood finishes & stained concrete flooring, a cat-walk, floor-to-ceiling fireplace with vaulted ceilings and exposed beams.
